headline: Motorola Solutions to Issue Third-Quarter 2025 Earnings Results on October 30
summary: CHICAGO, October 16, 2025--Motorola Solutions, Inc. (NYSE: MSI) will issue its third-quarter 2025 earnings results after the close of the market on Thursday, October 30.

headline: 3 Wireless Stocks Set to Ride on Solid 5G, Cloud & Fiber Adoption
summary: With solid demand for advanced networking architecture for increased broadband usage, the Zacks Wireless Equipment industry is likely to witness healthy growth. MSI, UI and IDCC are set to thrive on industry tailwinds.

headline: Motorola Solutions Advances AI-Assisted Policing
summary: CHICAGO, October 16, 2025--Motorola Solutions (NYSE: MSI) today announced it is giving Assist, the company’s public safety AI assistant, new capabilities to help officers do significantly more with less and accelerate operations. With Assist, officers can already redact voices and faces to protect privacy, translate in real-time while capturing a record of the conversation and find vehicles of interest with a simple description. Now, Assist will help enhance the thoroughness and speed of police
